The image depicts a large busted girl,  
dressed up in a bunny suit for Easter. She is facing to the right while  
looking at the viewer. SHe has bunny ears and a bunny tail. There is a  
small, long ear creature sticking out of her top, holding onto an easter  
egg. Her hair tassels have small rabbit heads on them.
